### ===============================================
### RESERVAESTUDIO — PROVEDOR DE RECEBIMENTO (STUDIO)
### ===============================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@studioId = REPLACE_STUDIO_ID
@subscriberToken = REPLACE_SUBSCRIBER_JWT

### Receber reservas via Mercado Pago (padrão) ou Stripe Connect
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/studios/{{studioId}}/payout-provider
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payoutProvider": "MERCADOPAGO"
}

### Escolher Stripe (exige Connect habilitado)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/studios/{{studioId}}/payout-provider
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payoutProvider": "STRIPE"
}
